795-445b-91da-9765523b1638-text-1"],"custom_css":[],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_7200f22b-9280-4abd-9457-a978183ee4bf.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"2cb68c65-93ce-4030-a625-5bac24b42fe4":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"2c2d5ff2-50f7-45b3-97a7-192755274d02":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>Wees zakkenrollers altijd een stap voor.<\/h3><p><br\/>Zorgen maken over zakkenrollers kan enorm vervelend zijn als je op reis bent, daarom beschikt de ROOLO Bag over geavanceerde antidiefstal functies<strong>, zodat je zorgeloos kunt reizen:<\/strong><\/p><p><br\/><strong>- Antidiefstal ritsen: <\/strong>Deze krijgen zakkenrollers niet eenvoudig open!<\/p><p><strong>- RFID-blokkeervakken: <\/strong>Deze vakken beschermen je auto sleutels, bankpassen, creditcards en zelfs paspoorten tegen elektronische diefstal!<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["2c2d5ff2-50f7-45b3-97a7-192755274d02"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/6g_2738a546-e8a1-4e00-9a55-f31c68fc7e6a.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"7ead9d52-a3ce-4f63-9e00-e5fbe252c5a8":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_tYUQWc":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading_size":"h2"}},"9bd8fb44-fa40-449d-be77-8f37af118496":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>De ROOLO Bag is je kluis in een slank formaat met een hoop ruimte.<\/p><p>Het heeft een <strong>slank ontwerp<\/strong>, met gemakkelijke toegang, robuust en is<strong> 100% waterdicht. <\/strong><\/p><p>Alles wat u nodig heeft, <strong>altijd bij de hand<\/strong>, zonder zorgen.<br\/><\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["heading_tYUQWc","9bd8fb44-fa40-449d-be77-8f37af118496"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Tas1.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"comparison_table_qncmkq":{"type":"comparison-table","blocks":{"row_JrRBw6":{"type":"row","settings":{"benefit":"Stekkers & USB","us":true,"others":false}},"row_r6nHWV":{"type":"row","settings":{"benefit":"Efficiënt  Design","us":true,"others":false}},"row_aJHnEM":{"type":"row","settings":{"benefit":"Overbelastingsbeveiliging","us":true,"others":false}},"row_qmB7DE":{"type":"row","settings":{"benefit":"Kabelbende","us":false,"others":true}}},"block_order":["row_JrRBw6","row_r6nHWV","row_aJHnEM","row_qmB7DE"],"custom_css":[],"settings":{"title":"Waarom deze stekkerdoos?","heading_size":"h2","text":"","button_label":"","link":"","button_style_secondary":false,"color_scheme":"background-1","layout":"table_second","us_label":"ROOLO","logo_width":90,"mobile_logo_width":60,"others_label":"Standaard","checkmark_color":"#53af01","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"image_with_text_83VBKw":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"text_Ai844A":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h4>Maat Tabel<\/h4><p>Bij twijfel raden wij aan om een maat groter te kiezen!<\/p><p><strong>LET OP: <\/strong>Houd de maattabel aan om de perfecte mat voor je 4 voeter uit te kiezen.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["text_Ai844A"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/MAAT_TABEL_82287e06-ae8c-44c7-b989-056407b009e8.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--19810270937412__01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3-collapsible_row-2":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Welke type moet ik kopen?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Kies voor rechterschouder als je de band op de rechterschouder wilt dragen en de tas aan de linkerkant (aanbevolen voor rechtshandigen).<br\/><br\/>Kies voor linkerschouder als je de band op de linkerschouder wilt dragen en de tas aan de rechterkant (aanbevolen voor linkshandigen).<\/p>","page":""}},"template--19810270937412__01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3-collapsible_row-3":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is de tas ook geschikt voor langere mensen?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Ja, de tas heeft een verstelbare draagband die ook geschikt is voor langere mensen.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--19810270937412__01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3-collapsible_row-4":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Past mijn telefoon in de tas?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Ja, vrijwel alle telefoons passen in de tas.<\/p>","page":""}},"a04138e4-e0c2-486d-a73f-15d028bcdff4":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Waarom is deze tas beter dan een rugzak?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Rugzakken zijn kwetsbaar voor diefstal en zakkenrollen, omdat ze op de rug gedragen worden en dieven niet snel gezien worden. Ze zijn ook groot en moeilijk te verplaatsen als ze vol zitten.<br\/><br\/>In deze tas draag je al je waardevolle spullen dicht bij je borst, zodat niemand anders dan jij erbij kan. Het heeft antidiefstal ritsen en RFID-blokkeerfuncties, zodat je met een gerust hart kan reizen en eindelijk van je tijd kangenieten.<\/p>","page":""}},"79c04b97-f82d-4831-a95e-b0904eb6a483":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Welke maten zijn er?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>De afmetingen zijn:<br\/><br\/>Lengte = 32 cm<br\/>Breedte = 2,5 cm<br\/>Hoogte = 23 cm<br\/><br\/>De tas heeft meerdere compartimenten waarin alles past wat je nodig hebt zonder dat het profiel te smal wordt<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["template--19810270937412__01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3-collapsible_row-2","template--19810270937412__01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3-collapsible_row-3","template--19810270937412__01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3-collapsible_row-4","a04138e4-e0c2-486d-a73f-15d028bcdff4","79c04b97-f82d-4831-a95e-b0904eb6a483"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"caption":"","heading_size":"h1","heading_alignment":"center","layout":"none","color_scheme":"background-1","container_color_scheme":"background-2","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"image_ratio":"adapt","desktop_layout":"image_second","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":36}},"66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19884972900676__66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>WAT KLANTEN OVER ONZE STEKKERDOOS ZEGGEN<br\/><\/h3><p>Nog niet overtuigd? Roolo heeft inmiddels ruim  <strong>4200+ tevreden klanten<\/strong>  en dat aantal groeit elke dag! <strong>Dit is wat klanten schrijven over onze Stekkerdoos:<\/strong>  <\/p><p><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19884972900676__66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0}},"1694520940915c1b12":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"0eb9aa84-d0ef-49a2-bc40-9002dcad3f09":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/judge-me-reviews\/blocks\/review_widget\/61ccd3b1-a9f2-4160-9fe9-4fec8413e5d8","settings":{}}},"block_order":["0eb9aa84-d0ef-49a2-bc40-9002dcad3f09"],"settings":{"include_margins":true}},"featured_collection_WQ4xP4":{"type":"featured-collection","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Meer voor je dierenvriend🐾","heading_size":"h1","description":"","show_description"